    Contact section:
    - Title changed to "Let's Connect"
    - Back button → "Gallery" with left arrow, sends flutter-handoff
    - Added Home button (bottom-right) → navigates to title screen
    - Added Audio toggle (bottom-right) → mutes/unmutes all Flutter audio
